      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, usable ride with tons of potential for someone who wants affordable transportation or a fun little project. A great chance to get into something at a sensible price without breaking the bank. If you appreciate a car with character and value, this one\u2019s definitely worth a look.",
